data.description: Classic 3500' full brick beauty with 4 large bedrooms & 2.5 baths in desirable Lakota Schools. No HOA! Family room with gas FP & walkout to  13x17 three seasons room overlooking lovely 18x36 inground pool. Large sunlit living room/office & dining. Eat-in kitchen w/desk & pantry. 1st fl laundry w/walk out to a gorgeous wooded lot. Partially finished LL. Updated 2nd floor baths. New roof 10/23, new 1st fl carpet 10/23. Anderson windows. Beautiful seasonal landscaping. Home is solid and very clean inside and out, well maintained!  Sold with full warranty.
